      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sorted E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This example is a true driver\u2019s car, equipped with a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been completed, including a reinforced rear subframe, VAC coated rod bearings, and a full Beisan Systems VANOS refresh. The suspension has been upgraded with Bilstein B16 coilovers, enhancing the chassis's lateral stiffness and turn-in response. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the drivetrain remains robust, delivering linear power and a visceral 8,000 RPM redline. Recent fluid analysis and a cooling system overhaul ensure this chassis is ready for spirited canyon carving or track day duties.",
